{"tid":2450324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"1.97萬失業大軍領綜援，按年飆近五成！","createTime":"2021-03-17T09:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T05:09:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"44e6fd3c1e7f9703fc123c879bf4823b8f86a1b1","tid":2450324,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T09:58:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20210317/mobile/odn-20210317-0317_00176_010.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210317%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20210317-0317_00176_010.html&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=9bf55d2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20210317/mobile/odn-20210317-0317_00176_010.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】因失業領取綜援的個案按年大增，社會福利署昨公布最新領取綜合社會保障援助（綜援）的個案數字，今年2月領取綜援的個案逾22.45萬宗，較1月微降517宗，按月跌幅為0.2%，受助總人數為31.8萬。<br />\n<br />\n2477低收入人士申請<br />\n<br />\n但因失業而領取綜援的個案則有1.97萬宗，按年升幅高達約49.5%；申請數字則按月下跌26.4%至683宗，較去年同月下跌5.7%。<br />\n<br />\n社署指出，低收入類別個案有2,477宗，按月跌幅為0.6%；年老類別個案下跌0.4%，有12.9萬宗。而健康欠佳類別個案則上升0.2%，至2.62萬宗；永久殘疾類別個案亦上升0.3%，有1.74萬宗；單親類別則保持平穩，有2.47萬宗。<br />\n<br />\n為支援失業人士，港府自去年中，放寬身體健全人士申領綜援的資產限額一年，至今年5月31日。另在今年《施政報告》提出，把身體健全人士的所有保險計劃現金價值豁免計算為資產。"},{"pid":"b77c93e066b0c15e9d1d1a8170f5fd2943be9df3","tid":2450324,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b794386b2a379ff2196880c708cb238afd0b888","tid":2450324,"uid":129676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>全民老綜,唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n救得一個得一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n★★★★★★★★★★綜援師精彩錄語★★★★★★★★★★<br />\n<br />\n[綜援師]講多無謂,如果對生活唔滿意,真係唔好撚做<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gJKCrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gJKCrS</a><br />\n<br />\n[正能量]有錢人最鐘意同你講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2441400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2441400</a><br />\n<br />\n[綜援師]莫信網上打手,教你破解進修騙局<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2443062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2443062</a>"},{"pid":"b5b7949726c8253c5180d0761477e690bde27aec","tid":2450324,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:14:30.000Z","msg":"@老貓"},{"pid":"e849c631172548939b89c194a5153a00c8aaacdb","tid":2450324,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:17:25.000Z","msg":"老綜無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e804d28c29964f58008e3a057763389cb762408f","tid":2450324,"uid":73991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"支持拎綜援，你唔拎就比班支拿狗拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bec2e854ac9e7afa4ee482654fe24291779b6f8","tid":2450324,"uid":133743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:20:41.000Z","msg":"有冇人知見社工會講啲咩<br />\n驚啲戲屎交唔到戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89b07b194c6a9d5b3af7f089d35ef0a7cce48fc","tid":2450324,"uid":219128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5bec2e854ac9e7afa4ee482654fe24291779b6f8","tid":2450324,"uid":133743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T04:20:41.000Z","msg":"有冇人知見社工會講啲咩<br />\n驚啲戲屎交唔到戲<img src=\"/ass